Method Detail

newInstance

IChangeEvent newInstance(IItem item)
Instantiates an IChangeEvent instance from the referenced item. The item, state, type name, type namespace, package, author and time field values are initialized from the referenced item - the time derived from the last modified time of the referenced item. The item is not persisted to any repository, and the server is not contacted.

Parameters:
item - The item to initialize the ChangeEvent from. May be null.
Returns:
The initialized ChangeEvent. Never null. The instantiated ChangeEvent is not persisted to the repository.
